subject: New Quikscript Font - kwikskript.zip

messageBody:
I have just uploaded a new Quikscript font called kwikskript.ttf (in
.zip format) into the font folder file. Initially, I accidentally
uploaded it into the general file area. Therefore, you may see 2
notifications that the file was uploaded.

The font is derived from the "Junior" font. However, it has been
greatly modified from that font, with a number of letters being
completely rebuilt. The basis of the modifications & rebuilds were on
the examples of letters in the Quikscript manual. This is a Junior
Quikscript font. The letters do not connect. All of the ligeratures &
basic letters are represented, as well as alternate-U & alternate-N.

Any questions or comments are welcome. Thank you.
